  <brief_title>Incidence of Infection After Total Knee Arthroplasty Using an Erythromycin and Colistin Loaded Cement or a Standard Cement</brief_title>
  <official_title>Incidence of Infection After Total Knee Arthroplasty Using an Erythromycin and Colistin Loaded Cement or a Standard Cement</official_title>
